bibleVerse: LORD, you have searched me and you know me. You know when I sit and when I risei you perceive my thoughts from afar. You discern my going out and my lying downi you are familiar with all my ways. Before a word is on my tongue you know it completely, O LORD. Psalm 139:1~4

No temptation has seized you except what is common to man. And God is faithfuli he will not le+ you be tempted beyond What you can bear. But when you are tempted, he will also provide a way out so that you can stand up under it. / corinthians 10:13
so, if you think you are standing firm, be careful that you don't fall! / cornthians 10:12
Show me your ways. O LORD. teach me your pathsi guide me in your truth and teach me. for you are God my savior. and my hope is in you all day long. Psalms 25:4~5
Do you not know that in a race all the runners run. but only one gets the prize? Run in such a way as to get the prize. / corinthians 9:24
